AA-181920 is a large droid from the depths of the desert. Once a drilling droid, he was abandoned when the caves he was drilling in collapsed, killing everyone inside. Unsure of his current directive or who is owner is, he stands in the corner of anchorhead and does nothing.

Nickkell, or Hood, is a merchant of Anchorhead that has a lot of weapons for sale. No one knows where or how he gets the weapons, they only know that they are all in good condition. Nickkell prides himself in his wares, although his weapons are well kept and maintained, the prices he has are sometimes ridiculous.

Lizemont Crowar, or Liz, is just another citizen of Anchorhead. Nothing special, just a generic woman. She loves cheese and enjoying a drink at the local bar. She often finds herself talking to random people and becomes quite a chatter box after a few drinks.
